            "content": "Write a short comparison of the meaning of the two sentences, writing a maximum of 5 sentences:\n\n## Sentence 1:\n\n> {sentenceWithTwoSynonyms}\n\n## Sentence 2:\n\n> {sentenceWithOriginalWordRemoved}",
